column5: So the deer season is almost over for another year. I havent got one yet but I took a poke at one 2 weeks ago and air mailed it over his back and blew it. Check out what has showed up at my stand in the last week.  If anyone is still goin at it good luck ill be in the stand new years eve Then its fishin time..
Haven't seen     all season, then tonight, just past legal shooting time, as i'm putting my bow in the case.  Buck and two does come moving toward me.  Maybe they'll be an hour early tomorrow..
It's tough waiting till the last week,but I'll be at it hard....in fact I'm leavin' now for the stand......Maybe today.........TC all ....Chuck...
Was supposed to go with the boy this morning but he's not feeling well and it's a cold north wind for the face in an open stand this morning. Friday will be my last chance after today.
